                  {
                    "value": "1. Standards & Contexts - choose Patient.race in the concept slicer (pilots filter = yes).",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontSize": "13pt",
                      "color": "#000000",
                      "fontFace": "Segoe UI"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "   Middle tables: left = CHI-approved standard codes; right = how partner values map to those codes.",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontSize": "13pt",
                      "color": "#000000",
                      "fontFace": "Segoe UI"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "   Then read FHIR R4 path above, and ADT (field_id + CE encoding) and C-CDA XPath below.",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontSize": "13pt",
                      "color": "#000000",
                      "fontFace": "Segoe UI"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "2. Repeat with Patient.language - ADT field_id should show PID-15 (hl7_ce_encoding may be blank).",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontSize": "13pt",
                      "color": "#000000",
                      "fontFace": "Segoe UI"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "3. Concept Profile - governance cards, survivorship, and source availability for the same concept.",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontSize": "13pt",
                      "color": "#000000",
                      "fontFace": "Segoe UI"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "4. Guide \u00b7 Field guide - filter by page or visual; steward_action shows which Excel sheet to edit.",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontSize": "13pt",
                      "color": "#000000",
                      "fontFace": "Segoe UI"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "5. Governance Overview - portfolio KPIs and full concept list (most rows are not yet curated).",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontSize": "13pt",
